k" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-=
decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color:=
 #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  October</a=
> about Avi Eisenberg, who exploited a decentralized finance protocol calle=
d Mango Markets for about $116 million, and then bragged about it, saying t=
hat =E2=80=9CI believe=C2=A0all of our actions were legal open market actio=
ns, using the protocol as designed, even if the development team did not fu=
lly anticipate all the consequences of setting parameters the way they are.=
=E2=80=9D Federal prosecutors did not agree, and he was arrested in Decembe=
r; we <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30334334.286=
518/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDEtMDM=
